DFLT     TITLE 'E X H I B I T  ***  DEFAULT SCREEN LAYOUT MODULE'
EXHLDFLT START 0
*
*        EXHLDFLT PROVIDES THE DEFAULT SCREEN LAYOUT, ALLOCATING SPACE
*        TO EACH OF EIGHT DISPLAY FUNCTIONS. THE NINTH ENTRY FOR
*        EXHDZZZZ IS MANDATORY , SINCE IT CONTROLS I/O TO THE CRT.
*
*        THREE SCREEN MAPPINGS ARE REQUIRED, ONE SET FOR EACH SUPPORTED
*        SCREEN SIZE.
*
*        EXHL MODULES ARE USED BY EXHAMODS IN RESPONSE TO A MODIFY
*        (LAYOUT= ) COMMAND, AND AT INITIALIZATION TIME FROM THE
*        EXEC CARD PARM FIELD AND/OR THE &LAYOUT OPTION.
*
         EJECT
*        TECHNION MAPPINGS
*
*        1920 BYTE SCREEN (IBM 3270)
*
         XODSP DA00,2,12,1,80,0        ROOM FOR 22 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,14,17,1,80,2       QUEUE SUMM: BOTH HASP & OS *TSM*
         XODSP DR00,18,20,1,80,1       REPLIES PENDING            *TSM*
         XODSP IR00,21,21,1,80,1       INTER., RQE & CPQE COUNTS  *TSM*
         XODSP MR00,22,24,1,80,1       MOUNT/AVR REQUESTS         *TSM*
         XODSP ON00,22,24,1,80,1       MOUNT/AVR REQUESTS         *TSM*
         XODSP PA00,13,13,1,80,1       PAGING STATISTICS          *TSM*
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,24,1,80,0  DISPLAY I/O
         SPACE 2
*        960 BYTE SCREEN (IBM 2260)
*
         XODSP DA00,1,5,1,80,0  ROOM FOR 10 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,6,7,1,80,2  18 QUEUE SUMM
         XODSP DR00,9,9,1,80,1  REPLIES
         XODSP IR00,8,8,1,40,1  INTERVENTION REQUESTS
         XODSP MR00,10,11,1,80,1  MOUNT/AVR REQUETS
         XODSP OF00,8,8,41,80,1   OFFLINE UNITS
         XODSP ON00,11,12,1,80,1   ONLINE DISKS
         XODSP PA00,00,00,0,00,255 NO ROOM FOR PAGE QUEUES       *TSM*
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,12,1,80,0  MANDATORY I/O ROUTINE
         SPACE 2
*        480 BYTE SCREEN (SMALL 3270 OR 2260)
*
         XODSP DA00,1,3,1,80,0   ROOM FOR 6 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,4,4,1,80,2   9 ENTRY QUEUE SUMMARY
         XODSP DR00,5,5,41,80,1    REPLIES
         XODSP IR00,5,5,21,40,1   INT. REQ.
         XODSP MR00,6,6,1,80,1   MOUNT/AVR REQUESTS
         XODSP OF00,5,5,1,20,1   OFFLINE INUTS
         XODSP ON00,6,6,41,80,1    ONLINE DISKS
         XODSP PA00,00,00,0,00,255 NO ROOM FOR PAGE QUEUES       *TSM*
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,6,1,80,0  I/O ROUTINE
         SPACE 2
EXHLEND  DS    0D            FOR SIZE TEST
         SIZER EXHLEND-EXHLDFLT,LAYOUT   TEST SIZE
         END
